title: Neil Young & Crazy Horse - 02 Arena, London, 17-6-2013
description:
Neil Young And Crazy Horse - 02 Arena, London, 17-6-2013.


This Is A Concert From The Alchemy Tour Performed At The 02 Arena, London On The Night OF The 17-6-2013. This Is Not An Official Release. I Created This Torrent By Sourcing As Many Different Versions Of Songs Recorded By Tapers At The Gig As Possible. I Then Chose The Best Versions Of Each Song Based On Audio / Video Quality And Edited Them, Cleaned Them Up And Placed Them In The Correct Order. I Hope You'll Agree That The Results Are Pretty Pretty Pretty, Pretty Good. I Was There And It Was An Amazing Show Which I'm Sure All Fans Of Neil And The Horse Will Love.


Enjoy, verydroll.
